  "title": "Introduction to Character Design",
  "lessonText": "Character design is the foundation of storytelling through visual art.",
  "data": {
    "content": "- Understand the purpose of character design.\n- Explore the elements that make a character memorable.\n- Learn about the role of personality in design.\n- Discover the importance of silhouette and shape.\n- Consider cultural influences on character design."
